jobs_results.description:
1. Identify and bridge payment service product gaps, prioritize, and continuously build and iterate products;
2. Work with legal, GR, PR, compliance, security to continuously improve TikTok Wallet and payment system to create a stable, agile and robust in-app wallet system;
3. Closely monitor all business endpoints' payment status, analyze the daily data and cope with urgent requests;
4. Integrate with Tax, KYC (know your customer), order system to support all business endpoints on TikTok Platform;
5. Create a central platform to support TikTok internal teams to better operate TikTok Wallet system, to ensure smooth and seamless pay-out execution.
1. Excellent communication skills, can clearly describe the vision, planning and problem; and coordinate with other teams to solve it together in depth;
2. 3+ years of product management experience building payment/wallet product
3. User-first mindset with high attention to details
4. Entrepreneurship, able to deal with rapid changes and... imperfect status quo;
5. Has a global vision and enthusiasm, and pays continuous attention to global internet products;
6. Fluency in English, mandarin is a plus
